%The analysis code that was used in: Vetter P., Bola L., Reich L., Bennett M., Muckli L., Amedi A. (2020). Decoding natural sounds in early “visual” cortex of congenitally blind individuals. Current Biology.%The code was originally created by Fraser W. Smith (see Smith & Muckli 2010 PNAS)and was adapted to this project by Petra Vetter and Lukasz Bola.function [renormalized,out] = stretch(image, varargin)% [renormalized] = Stretch(image, [min, max]).  If not specified, min = 0 and max = 1.if (nargin > 3)	error('Wrong number of arguments.');endminValue = 0;range = 1;if (nargin == 3)	minValue = varargin{1:1};	range = abs(varargin{2:2} - varargin{1:1});end im = double(image);renormalized = range * (im - min(min(im))) ./ (max(max(im)) - min(min(im))) + minValue;out=[min(min(im)) max(max(im))];